<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Greer</ENAMEX>, <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Clive Jenkins</ENAMEX>, and <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Janet Street-Porter</ENAMEX>)
whose direct connection with the book at hand would
