the <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">editors</ENAMEX>.  But <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">only four</NUMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">editors</ENAMEX> for such a massive
work?  I suppose it is possible.  In any event, it seems
