            The <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">L</ENAMEX> was based on the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">W</ENAMEX> , but a comparison,
albeit superficial, reveals a number of differences,
to wit:

            
<NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">1</NUMEX>.  The headword is syllabified in <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">W</ENAMEX> , not in <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">L</ENAMEX> .  In
